Rating: 3
Very tasty. The flavors all work well together, although I suspect the brandy would not be missed, and it's sweet without being cloying. I added a light sprinkling of salt, but otherwise followed the recipe as written. I used the garnet yams as specified and liked both their flavor and the fact that they didn't get mushy and fall apart. This may make a reappearance accompanying ham at my Christmas Eve dinner.